{"title":"wtc_rsa_bbq","slug":"wtc_rsa","date":"2021-01-30T01:19:52.189Z","updated":"2021-01-30T01:30:52.635Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/wtc_rsa.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":null,"covers":["https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210130091434198.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjIyNzAxNg==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center"],"content":"<p><a href=\"https://adworld.xctf.org.cn/task/answer?type=crypto&number=5&grade=1&id=4758&page=1\">wtc_rsa_bbq</a></p>\n<p>得到一个二进制文件和一个.pem公钥文件，通过利用openssl可以得到，rsa的公钥和私钥，<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210130091434198.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjIyNzAxNg==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>其中e=65537，但是公钥很长，但是因为数的后面为均为ff，可以猜测n为一个数乘一个2的次幂，所有可以计算得到p和q</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"title\">isqrt</span>(<span class=\"params\">n</span>):</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  x = n</span><br><span class=\"line\">  y = (x + n // x) // <span class=\"number\">2</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">while</span> y &lt; x:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    x = y</span><br><span class=\"line\">    y = (x + n // x) // <span class=\"number\">2</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> x</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">n = <span class=\"number\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">e = <span class=\"number\">65537</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">i = isqrt(n)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">p, q = <span class=\"number\">0</span>, <span class=\"number\">0</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">while</span> <span class=\"literal\">True</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> n - (i * (n // i)) == <span class=\"number\">0</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    p = i</span><br><span class=\"line\">    q = n//i</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">break</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  i += <span class=\"number\">1</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">print</span> (p)</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">print</span> (q)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>得到p和q以后就可以计算出私钥，进而得到明文</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> gmpy2</span><br><span class=\"line\">n = gmpy2.mpz(<span class=\"number\"></span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">p = gmpy2.mpz(<span class=\"number\"></span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">q = gmpy2.mpz(<span class=\"number\"></span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">e = <span class=\"number\">65537</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#cipher = open(r&#x27;D:\\CTF\\problem\\2021\\0126\\wtc\\cry200\\cipher.bin&#x27;, &#x27;rb&#x27;).read().encode(&#x27;hex&#x27;)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">cipher=<span class=\"number\"></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">fi = (p-<span class=\"number\">1</span>)*(q-<span class=\"number\">1</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">d = gmpy2.invert(e, fi)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">flag = gmpy2.powmod(cipher, d, n)</span><br><span class=\"line\">flag=<span class=\"built_in\">int</span>(flag)</span><br><span class=\"line\">print(<span class=\"built_in\">hex</span>(flag))</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>然后转成对应的字符即可。</p>\n","categories":[],"tags":[]}